MODIFICATIONS
  The following automated modifications were made to adapt the project
  for the Zcash network:
  - Module/directory renames (e.g. bitcoin/ → zcash/)
  - Network parameter updates (ports, DNS seeds, binary names)
  - Class renames (e.g. CBitcoinAddress → CZcashAddress)
  - Currency references (BTC → ZEC, satoshis → zatoshis)

  All original copyright headers and license notices are preserved.
  No original license terms were modified or removed.
